(19644, 'Gemcitabine actavis 200mg i.v.vial(n/a)', 'جيمسيتابين اكتافيس 200 مجم فيال', '', '154', 'Gemcitabine', 'Actavis > multipharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antineoplastic', '200mg', 'Gemcitabine is a chemotherapeutic agent used as monotherapy or in combination with other anticancer agents. 
